fields.title: Neuromancer
fields.description: Winner of the Hugo, Nebula, and Philip K. Dick Awards, Neuromancer is a science fiction masterpiece — a classic that ranks as one of the twentieth century’s most potent visions of the future.

fields.title: Mona Lisa Overdrive
fields.description: William Gibson, author of the extraordinary multiaward-winning novel Neuromancer, has written his most brilliant and thrilling work to date . . .The Mona Lisa Overdrive.
